<div class="container">
    <h2>Introduction</h2>
    <p>
        Body balance means maintaining both physical and mental health in a proper way.
        Sustainability for body balance includes healthy food, regular exercise, enough sleep,
        hydration, stress control, and positive thinking. Small daily habits help create a strong,
        active, and healthy life.
    </p>

    <h2>Important Points for Body Balance</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Eat healthy and balanced food daily</li>
        <li>Drink 2–3 liters of water every day</li>
        <li>Exercise regularly like walking, yoga, or cycling</li>
        <li>Sleep for 7–8 hours every night</li>
        <li>Maintain good posture while sitting and walking</li>
        <li>Avoid stress and practice meditation</li>
        <li>Spend time outdoors and take sunlight</li>
        <li>Stay positive and manage time properly</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Conclusion</h2>
    <p>
        Sustainability for body balance is achieved through regular healthy habits.
        It improves energy, fitness, mental peace, and discipline. A balanced body leads
        to a better and happier life.
    </p>
